https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vtB1J_zCv8I

tmux 

open new window
ctrl + b + c 

vertical panel spliting 
ctrl + b + shift + "

Horizontal panel spliting
ctrl + b + shift + %

to close one single panel
Press Ctrl-b, then x.
tmux will prompt: kill-pane? (y/n).

to navigate panels in tmux 
ctrl + b, arrow keys 
